{"tid":601433,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本家長最不希望小孩當YouTuber","createTime":"2018-03-22T08:18:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-22T16:22:36.000Z","uid":75969,"like":136,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"f72ca4fca4a67d39408879e7c17eafcb7dd15754","tid":601433,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:18:14.000Z","msg":"網絡直播漸成職業，很多小學生的志願是當YouTuber。甚至有日本機構開辦YouTuber教室，從小培養出色的直播員。根據去年兵庫縣立大學進行的調查，最多大阪府小學生希望成為足球選手，其次是醫生和YouTuber。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.ytimg.com/vi/DFCApP66o14/maxresdefault.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.ytimg.com%2Fvi%2FDFCApP66o14%2Fmaxresdefault.jpg&h=2d34c3a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，據保險公司ソニー生命近日公布的調查，男子中學生最想當程式員、遊戲設計師和YouTuber。原來在這幾年裡，YouTuber成為了孩子們憧憬的存在。可是，父母對YouTuber的印象就沒有那麼正面。<br />\n<br />\n日前，日媒「日刊SPA!」向100位30歲以上的父母進行調查，發現他們最不希望子女將來成為YouTuber(59%)，其次的營業員只佔11%，反映家長不認同YouTuber是一個理想職業。他們反對孩子當YouTuber的主要理由是工作收入不穩定，以及職業無法持續一生。媽媽受訪者認為YouTuber都是一些自戀狂，靠做一些蠢事來增加點擊率和提高名氣；爸爸受訪者就希望子女能對社會作出貢獻，而非當眾人的小丑。<br />\n<br />\n▼ YouTuber教室的上課重點是如何提高點擊率<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://livedoor.blogimg.jp/yabanet/imgs/e/4/e4e282f3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Flivedoor.blogimg.jp%2Fyabanet%2Fimgs%2Fe%2F4%2Fe4e282f3.jpg&h=6e001408&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<a href=\"https://nikkan-spa.jp/1462289/2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnikkan-spa.jp%2F1462289%2F2&d=jYQxgPNCiBBMWRoR2vEy0AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=934e1738\" target=\"_blank\">https://nikkan-spa.jp/1462289/2</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://japhub.com/?c=7157\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fjaphub.com%2F%3Fc%3D7157&d=jYQxgPNCiBBMWRoR2vEy0AdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=1a8f9de3\" target=\"_blank\">http://japhub.com/?c=7157</a>"},{"pid":"e35e0b34fe9ab5911a8d5540ce046acbf44f0bef","tid":601433,"uid":75969,"like":228,"dislike":8,"score":220,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"媽媽受訪者認為YouTuber都是一些自戀狂，靠做一些蠢事來增加點擊率和提高名氣；爸爸受訪者就希望子女能對社會作出貢獻，而非當眾人的小丑。<br />\n<br />\n即係做藝人都唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45aae5c8cb372f6aa699d8aa02ed55dc4bc57c2e","tid":601433,"uid":113626,"like":25,"dislike":72,"score":-47,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:19:09.000Z","msg":"連登已經開始懷念伍公子<br />\n好快youtuber會係連登神職業之一"},{"pid":"beb217b9d352d2a1b7897240631e36ab1f088607","tid":601433,"uid":34010,"like":36,"dislike":1,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:20:06.000Z","msg":"打死一世牛工最穩定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e82e858c20238135f912f23cc4209b7bad9a95c1","tid":601433,"uid":116530,"like":3,"dislike":11,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:20:14.000Z","msg":"第一幅圖係邊個YouTuber <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29f4c51b1e346a48f8ec177e4cdb3125b483be07","tid":601433,"uid":2959,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:20:53.000Z","msg":"香港只會當兼職咁做"},{"pid":"1d4607be1f9b5c3b14226f68d544988616c70c22","tid":601433,"uid":24345,"like":42,"dislike":3,"score":39,"quote":{"pid":"e35e0b34fe9ab5911a8d5540ce046acbf44f0bef","tid":601433,"uid":75969,"like":228,"dislike":8,"score":220,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"媽媽受訪者認為YouTuber都是一些自戀狂，靠做一些蠢事來增加點擊率和提高名氣；爸爸受訪者就希望子女能對社會作出貢獻，而非當眾人的小丑。<br />\n<br />\n即係做藝人都唔得?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:21:49.000Z","msg":"拎藝人同youtuber 比<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65a68864535ebe13e726d5163adce78aa4551a0c","tid":601433,"uid":130897,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"第二張圖咩料<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe6415d6e8527414735daadbfb20e4e7700cd43d","tid":601433,"uid":63846,"like":55,"dislike":15,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-22T08:33:22.000Z","msg":"